nt de vous rendre en gare.<br><br>Pour plus d&#8217;informations rendez vous sur le Blog Ligne L.<\/p>","shortMessage":"Trafic perturbé","disruption_id":"07cf81ec-b694-4d71-a91e-ed8660723971"},{"id":"449628ed-3c23-4ee7-9554-5c5f59d78fb3","applicationPeriods":[{"begin":"20260619T051400","end":"20260619T170000"}],"lastUpdate":"20260619T115314","cause":"PERTURBATION","severity":"PERTURBEE","title":"Tramway  T4 : Trafic fortement perturbé sur toute la ligne","message":"<p>Le trafic est fortement perturbé sur toute la ligne T4.<br>&nbsp;<\/p><p>Motif : Conditions de départ non réunies.<\/p><p>Prévoir des retards et des prolongations de temps de trajets.<\/p><p>&nbsp;<\/p><p>Veuillez nous excuser pour la gêne occasionnée.<\/p>","disruption_id":"921243e3-3b9f-4ea1-abef-b113ada9eead"},{"id":"d7db7709-1ba6-42b3-a130-a0aee9c0bdd7","applicationPeriods":[{"begin":"20260601T044500","end":"20260901T043000"}],"lastUpdate":"20260601T044619","cause":"TRAVAUX","severity":"BLOQUANTE","tags":["Actualité"],"title":"Tramway T1 : Travaux de modernisation - Trafic interrompu","message":"<p>Jusqu'au 31 août inclus, le trafic est interrompu entre Gare de Noisy-le-Sec et Bobigny – Pablo Picasso en raison de travaux de modernisation.<br>Bus de remplacement.<\/p>","shortMessage":"Trafic interrompu","impactedSections":[{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01389","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:72041","name":"Noisy-le-Sec (Noisy-le-Sec)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:72486","name":"Bobigny - Pablo Picasso (Bobigny)"}},{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01389","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:72486","name":"Bobigny - Pablo Picasso (Bobigny)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:72041","name":"Noisy-le-Sec (Noisy-le-Sec)"}}],"disruption_id":"ab25bed8-00b3-4404-b4f2-7efb542de554"},{"id":"fb6cb1bf-d516-46d2-a991-607498c44686","applicationPeriods":[{"begin":"20260612T030000","end":"20260620T030000"}],"lastUpdate":"20260615T221645","cause":"PERTURBATION","severity":"PERTUR